      • getClassWeight

        public double getClassWeight(int i)
        The classWeights can be passed in as a comma separated list of weights using the -classWeights flag. If the classWeights are not specified, the value is assumed to be 1.0. classWeights only apply at train time; we do not weight the classes at all during test time.
